{"tid":258943,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[開箱]INORI PROJECT","createTime":"2017-05-26T14:00:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-31T10:40:40.000Z","uid":66532,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d4f0e36ac40416901ccc5651e22604090127bce5","tid":258943,"uid":66532,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T14:00:13.000Z","msg":"想知道連登有冇巴絲同好都訂咗依本畫冊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n是噉的，小弟今年一月嗰時見到TOM Project有得訂依本畫冊<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/26/213818_8ede3cccb6aebd3bacb7f8425936cf66.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F26%2F213818_8ede3cccb6aebd3bacb7f8425936cf66.jpg&h=72b9988b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n掙扎左一段時間，因為真係好貴，結果搞到二月嗰時先落訂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n四月尾左右發貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知parcel force worldwide班hihi扣起咗個畫冊收tax<br />\n其實本來都知要tax嫁啦，但係等咗將近成個月都未收到信，結果要打封email畀佢哋問下發生咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後就喺噚日，終於到咗啦<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/26/214214_f56e091ceceb5908036941a11b6fcc75.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F26%2F214214_f56e091ceceb5908036941a11b6fcc75.jpg&h=02e77ff2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個箱差唔多成米高<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔講仲以為買畫冊送紙皮盒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後開咗個箱之後，入面就有三樣野<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/26/214557_287990d2ce6554b0f29c6ed12ec5eabb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F26%2F214557_287990d2ce6554b0f29c6ed12ec5eabb.jpg&h=fd230f4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n分別係 畫冊 掛畫 同 poster<br />\n<br />\n首先就梗係開咗個畫冊嚟睇先啦<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/26/214703_d8f1e73773082b7d456c1248c2d3e76c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F26%2F214703_d8f1e73773082b7d456c1248c2d3e76c.jpg&h=05c9ad4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n畫冊編號<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/26/214736_822948d92b77283652e3625e82b48577.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F26%2F214736_822948d92b77283652e3625e82b48577.jpg&h=0195cc54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲送埋一塊布（我估用嚟抹塵用？<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/26/214823_abc70a806e8d3610e351c9419ce80055.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F26%2F214823_abc70a806e8d3610e351c9419ce80055.jpg&h=4dec2c82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本畫冊嘅封面同封底都係用亞加力膠板，所以摸上手本野好硬淨<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/26/215253_e8014cd7142075f8e8123989373cf790.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F26%2F215253_e8014cd7142075f8e8123989373cf790.jpg&h=7d8b6dd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n入面大部redjuice 嘅畫網上都有嘅，我就po一兩張算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/26/215022_c4bd2a0884703c478935550139891c27.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F26%2F215022_c4bd2a0884703c478935550139891c27.jpg&h=24eeb430&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/26/215054_58a0c4a29929a79000b1a9c8a5d2e420.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F26%2F215054_58a0c4a29929a79000b1a9c8a5d2e420.jpg&h=8c085f0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後就係幅掛畫<br />\n老實講，我冇諗過幅野係噉大幅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/26/215406_657041d5424ecd5a381adb94d760036c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F26%2F215406_657041d5424ecd5a381adb94d760036c.jpg&h=84429242&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n喺度煩緊點拎翻香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為怕整花幅掛畫，所以我就冇拆到啲啪啪紙啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n開箱文大概就係噉啦<br />\n如果覺得我打字1999，還望見諒<br />\n用手機排版，可能會好亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b65913e74d454628e886df4e4e5870db2fa8617","tid":258943,"uid":20941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T14:01:41.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d835d7331cad3df1f314baa6390fb44ba6abf7c3","tid":258943,"uid":30673,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T15:18:17.000Z","msg":"乳交服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f420006217d9ea61cca99518b550d53eabbb2df","tid":258943,"uid":66532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T15:56:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乳交服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 金魚服"},{"pid":"f16f9810559852046b57353ec8cdf7ecdbf2581f","tid":258943,"uid":30673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T16:14:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>乳交服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 金魚服</blockquote><br />\n乳交服(金魚skin)"},{"pid":"aca2fe69e0ed7958b3a9304aef2f84d60b6e8a5c","tid":258943,"uid":1354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T05:49:53.000Z","msg":"幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7d013f4a7e6daad040190e19b1e4529b4b5d4ea","tid":258943,"uid":7977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T07:08:59.000Z","msg":"祈妹好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e074d9013723ca6510193d14541493efec6e2144","tid":258943,"uid":1678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T07:11:11.000Z","msg":"買完冇位放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91e4b9f708573be2b660fff3b51590e0fe0104b1","tid":258943,"uid":104380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T07:15:29.000Z","msg":"點運返香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88b14c7391844bb9a6991906c8c6c95503121472","tid":258943,"uid":66532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T03:30:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我買咗&yen;70,000<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係就係貴咗啲，但真係唔錯"},{"pid":"7d8c716c2e0dc170128d7e975bd0783cec370b9a","tid":258943,"uid":66532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T03:35:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點運返香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我之前同朋友去日本玩，佢買咗部高達模型(用真鐵嚟造把刀嗰隻)，上機之前唔使加錢有得寄倉。<br />\n我兩星期後撘BA，唔知有冇得走盞拎上機(A380)？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最差情況就要寄倉，仲要label埋fragile，希望地勤人員可以輕手啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caac32da7755bfc6fb151465ef55e810b75adbfa","tid":258943,"uid":58623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T03:38:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我買咗&yen;70,000<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係就係貴咗啲，但真係唔錯</blockquote><br />\n本來都有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但聽完你講價錢之後<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d535cbbec5835f7e226aa72b888abffe9da490f","tid":258943,"uid":37890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T04:23:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我買咗&yen;70,000<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係就係貴咗啲，但真係唔錯</blockquote><br />\n本來都有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但聽完你講價錢之後<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係好撚貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除2都會諗下"},{"pid":"e710ec7db9840d87d613516ce9dbef129e4ec242","tid":258943,"uid":66532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T10:40:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我買咗&yen;70,000<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係就係貴咗啲，但真係唔錯</blockquote><br />\n本來都有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但聽完你講價錢之後<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實佢有好多版本，我買嗰個係最貴嗰個噉解姐，平到萬幾兩萬&yen;快都有"},{"pid":"55a3ebdf9403b10768e05aca091c7bce564b1451","tid":258943,"uid":66532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T10:40:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我買咗&yen;70,000<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係就係貴咗啲，但真係唔錯</blockquote><br />\n本來都有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但聽完你講價錢之後<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實佢有好多版本，我買嗰個係最貴嗰個噉解姐，平到萬幾兩萬&yen;都有</blockquote>"}]}